<%@ Page Title="Seiha Global Academy/Procedure" Language="C#" MasterPageFile="~/Site.Master" AutoEventWireup="true" CodeBehind="Procedure.aspx.cs" Inherits="WebApplication1.Procedure" %>


<asp:Content runat="server" ID="BodyContent" ContentPlaceHolderID="MainContent">

    <section class="PlanPage">
        <div class="video-overlay1 header-text">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="container-courseC">
                  <h1><strong>Procedure and Preparation</strong> </h1>
                
            </div>
            <div class="container-mainCourse">
                
                <div class="container-Procedure" style="padding:20px;">
                      <div class="row">
                          <div class="col-lg-12" style="text-align:center;">
                              <div class="accordion" data-panelid="panel1">
                                  <div class="boxProcedure1" style="background-color:#afeeee;">
                                    <h1 style="color:#000;font-size:24px;font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;">01</h1>
                                      
                                  </div>
                              <div class="boxProcedure2" style="border:2px solid #afeeee;">
                                  <h4>COURSE REGISTRATION<i class="fa fa-plus-circle iconClass" style="font-size:26px;float:right;"></i></h4> 
                                                                   
                              </div>
                              </div>
                              <div class="panel" id="panel1" style="background-color:#e0ffff;">
                                  <p>Complete the application form for study abroad online at sga.com/Bookin. Once done, one of our customer representatives will contact the number you provided within 25 hours to confirm that all details that are given are true or correct.</p>   
                              </div>
                              
                         </div>
                          <div class="col-lg-12" style="text-align:center;margin-top:30px;">
                            <div class="accordion" data-panelid="panel2">
                              <div class="boxProcedure1"  style="background-color:#ffc0cb;">
                                  <h1 style="color:#000;font-size:24px;font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;">02</h1>
                              </div>
                              <div class="boxProcedure2" style="border:2px solid #ffc0cb;">
                                  <h4>REGISTRATION AND TUITION FEE <i class="fa fa-plus-circle iconClass" style="font-size:26px;float:right;"></i></h4>
                                  
                              </div>
                            </div>
                              <div class="panel" id="panel2" style="background-color:#ffe4e1;">
                                  <p>Pay the registration fee of USD 125 and the tuition fee for the chosend study plan and curriculum. Wait for the invoice to be sent to your e-mail provided within 2-3 working days.</p>   
                              </div>
                         </div>
                          <div class="col-lg-12" style="text-align:center;margin-top:30px;">
                              <div class="accordion" data-panelid="panel3">
                                      <div class="boxProcedure1" style="background-color:#fff6a1">
                                          <h1 style="color:#000;font-size:24px;font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;">03</h1>
                                      </div>
                                      <div class="boxProcedure2" style="border:2px solid #fff6a1;">
                                          <h4>FLIGHT SCHEDULE <i class="fa fa-plus-circle iconClass" style="font-size:26px;float:right;"></i></h4>
                                      </div>
                              </div>
                              <div class="panel" id="panel3" style="background-color:#fbf8d7;">
                                  <p>It is important to book a flight 2 months or earlier prior to your desired departure date. There are times when it is difficult to reserve a slot, especially during peak season. <br />PEAK SEASON: March to May, July to August, December to January</p>   
                              </div>
                         </div>
                          <div class="col-lg-12" style="text-align:center;margin-top:30px;">
                              <div class="accordion" data-panelid="panel4">
                                  <div class="boxProcedure1" style="background-color:#66d6fc;">
                                      <h1 style="color:#000;font-size:24px;font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;">04</h1>
                                  </div>
                                  <div class="boxProcedure2" style="border:2px solid #66d6fc;">
                                      <h4>PAYMENT CONFIRMATION <i class="fa fa-plus-circle iconClass" style="font-size:26px;float:right;"></i></h4>
                                      
                                  </div>
                              </div>
                              <div class="panel" id="panel4"  style="background-color:#caeaf5;">
                                  <p>Make sure to settle all payments before your departure date, If tuition fee is not fully paid within 3 week prior to departure date, the registration will be cancelled.</p>   
                              </div>
                         </div>
                          <div class="col-lg-12" style="text-align:center;margin-top:30px;">
                              <div class="accordion" data-panelid="panel5">
                                  <div class="boxProcedure1" style="background-color:#dcb6dc;">
                                      <h1 style="color:#000;font-size:24px;font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;">05</h1>
                                  </div>
                                  <div class="boxProcedure2" style="border:2px solid #dcb6dc;">
                                      <h4>ORIENTATION <i class="fa fa-plus-circle iconClass" style="font-size:26px;float:right;"></i></h4>
                                      
                                  </div>
                              </div>
                              <div class="panel" id="panel5" style="background-color:#e6e0e6;">
                                  <p>Once flight details are confirmed. you will receive a departure orientation from our customer representative. At this time, the pick up schedule in Cebu is determined based on the flight information that you will give.</p>   
                              </div>
                         </div>
                          <div class="col-lg-12" style="text-align:center;margin-top:30px;">
                              <div class="accordion" data-panelid="panel6">
                                  <div class="boxProcedure1" style="background-color:#afda57;">
                                      <h1 style="color:#000;font-size:24px;font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;">06</h1>
                                  </div>
                                  <div class="boxProcedure2" style="border:2px solid #afda57;">
                                      <h4>PREPATION FOR DEPARTURE <i class="fa fa-plus-circle iconClass" style="font-size:26px;float:right;"></i></h4>
                                      
                                  </div>
                              </div>
                              <div class="panel" id="panel6" style="background-color:#eae8d3;">
                                  <p>This includes travel insurance, international debit card, currency exchange, check list of </p>  
                              </div>
                         </div>
                          <div class="col-lg-12" style="text-align:center;margin-top:30px;">
                              <div class="accordion" data-panelid="panel7">
                                  <div class="boxProcedure1" style="background-color:#cbc68b;">
                                      <h1 style="color:#000;font-size:24px;font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;">07</h1>
                                  </div>
                                  <div class="boxProcedure2" style="border:2px solid #cbc68b;">
                                      <h4>DEPARTURE <i class="fa fa-plus-circle iconClass" style="font-size:26px;float:right;"></i></h4>
                                      
                                  </div>
                              </div>
                              <div class="panel" id="panel7" style="background-color:#eae8d3;">
                                  <p>You must be at the airport at least 2 hours before departrure and stay at your airline's counter. It normally takes about few hours to get to Cebu depending on which country or city you come from When you arrive, you need to fill out the immigration form distributed by the cabin crew on the plane.</p>   
                              </div>
                         </div>
                          <div class="col-lg-12" style="text-align:center;margin-top:30px;">
                              <div class="accordion" data-panelid="panel8">
                                  <div class="boxProcedure1" style="background-color:#afeeee;">
                                      <h1 style="color:#000;font-size:24px;font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;">08</h1>
                                  </div>
                                  <div class="boxProcedure2" style="border:2px solid #afeeee;">
                                      <h4>ARRIVAL <i class="fa fa-plus-circle iconClass" style="font-size:26px;float:right;"></i></h4>
                                  
                                  </div>
                              </div>
                              <div class="panel" id="panel8" style="background-color:#e0ffff;">
                                  <p>Once you arrive at Mactan-Cebu International Airport, you will see of the Seiha Global Academy (SGA) staff holding an SGA placard on the right side of the airport building. SGA will arrange the transportation that will take you to your hotel. Also, you will be given a schedule and some instruction for next day.</p>   
                              </div>
                         </div>
                      </div>
                </div>
            </div>  
       </div>
    </section>
    <style>
.accordion {
 
  color: #444;
  cursor: pointer;
  padding: 0;
  width: 100%;
  border: none;
  margin:0;
  outline: none;
  font-size: 15px;
  transition: 0.4s;
  
}


.panel {
  padding:10px 30px 20px 30px;
  /*background-color: #afda57;*/
  width:60%;
  margin:0px auto;
  max-height: 110px;
  overflow: hidden;
  display:none;
  transition: max-height 0.2s ease-out;
  
}
</style>
 <script>
     $(function () {
         $('.accordion').on('click', function () {
             var panelId = $(this).attr('data-panelid');
             $('#' + panelId).slideToggle();
             var icon = $(this).find('.iconClass');
             icon.toggleClass('fa-plus-circle fa-minus-circle');
         });

     });
</script>

</asp:Content>
